name: Drone Spree - gray days
description: Drone Spree joined Lala Laboratories at a young age.  She passed all physical and phycological tests during the Drone Integration program.  Unfortunately, Drone Spree was the target of extreme hazing, and had to leave her original post to be moved into the Legal Sector.  There, she was able to move up in ranks, and with a stoke of a pen, and the pounding of a stamp, she got her revenge on all Drones that had done her wrong.
